===Etymology 1===
{{WikiSaurus-link|new}}
From Old French [[novel#Old French|novel]] (modern [[nouvel]]), from Latin [[novellus]], from [[novus]] ‘new’.

====Adjective====
{{en-ad|novel}}

# [[new]], [[original]], especially in an interesting way

